Function Reference/wp get sidebars widgets « WordPress Codex
-----------

Retrieve full list of [sidebars](/Sidebars "Sidebars") and their
widgets.

Will upgrade sidebar widget list, if needed. Will also save updated
list, if needed.

Parameters
----------

 `$deprecated` 
:   ([*boolean*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Boolean "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Not used (deprecated).
    Default: true

Return Values
-------------

 `` `(array)`{style="color:gray"} 
:   Upgraded list of widgets to version 3 array format when called from
    the admin.

Change Log
----------

Since: [2.2](/Version_2.2 "Version 2.2")

Source File
-----------

wp\_get\_sidebars\_widgets() is located in `wp-includes/widgets.php`

